      "type": "Evidence",
      "name": "Synthesis of prior hemolysis CFD validation studies",
      "description": "A comprehensive synthesis of multiple prior peer-reviewed studies examining CFD-based hemolysis prediction in rotary blood pumps, including the Goubergrits & Affeld (2004) power-law calibration, the Hariharan et al. (2011) FDA pump round-robin, and the Malinauskas et al. (2017) interlaboratory comparison. This node aggregates findings across experimental platforms, mesh strategies, and turbulence model choices to establish the evidentiary basis for model form selection and validation adequacy claims in the current COU."
